# AI Coach

Central feature, not a side panel. Full spec: @docs/AI_COACH.md

- `POST /api/coach` — middleware-protected, streams via Vercel AI SDK + `claude-sonnet-4-6`.
- System prompt in `apps/web/lib/coach-prompt.ts`. Context built server-side from Supabase.
- Persist to `coach_messages`. Warm mentor tone; never shame or score.
- `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` server-side only.
